TITLE Pure Water with NaCl Addition, and a useful output!
SOLUTION 1
    units   mol/kgw
    temp    25.0
    pH      7.0
    pe      4.0
    redox   pe
    units   mol/kgw
    density 1.0
    water   1.0 # kg

REACTION
    NaCl    1.0
    1 moles in 100 steps

SELECTED_OUTPUT 
    -file <<OUTPUT FILE>>
    -totals  Na Cl
    -activities Na+ Cl-

END